# Getting `Article with that name already exists.` What does that mean?
## What?
This means that another article already has this name.
## How to resolve this problem
Choose another title.
> Tip: You can go to the home page of [Articles](articles/) to 
> see the existing article titles. Use your browser's search 
> or find on page feature to find an existing title.
>
> Titles are __case sensitive__!
title: Article with that name already exists
